FuncDef: This command remove UPnP mappings for the specified subscriber. Ifprotocolandoutside-portare not specified, then all UPnP mappings of subscriber will be removed.
CLIs: upnp-mappings subscriber <sub-ident-string> protocol { tcp | udp } outside-port <port-number>

ParaDef.Info: clears mappings for the specified subscriber.
Clears the mappings for the specified protocol.
Clears mappings for the specified outside-port.
